      {"type":"code-puzzle","question":"Составьте settings.json с env и permissions","items":["{","  \"permissions\": {","    \"allow\": [\"Edit\", \"Bash(npm test)\"]","  },","  \"env\": {","    \"ANTHROPIC_MODEL\": \"claude-sonnet-4-20250514\"","  }","}"]},
      {"type":"multi-select","question":"Что можно настроить в settings.json?","options":[{"id":"a","text":"Разрешения (permissions)","correct":True},{"id":"b","text":"Переменные окружения (env)","correct":True},{"id":"c","text":"MCP-серверы (mcpServers)","correct":True},{"id":"d","text":"Хуки (hooks)","correct":True},{"id":"e","text":"Цвет интерфейса (theme)","correct":False}]},
