      {"type":"terminal-sim","prompt":"Проверьте состояние окружения Claude Code","expectedCommand":"/doctor","output":"Environment check:\n  ✓ Node.js v20.11.0\n  ✓ npm v10.2.4\n  ✓ Git v2.43.0\n  ✓ Claude Code v1.0.20\n  ✓ Authentication valid\n  ✓ 2 MCP servers connected","hint":"Используйте /doctor для диагностики"},
